snippet.description:

Experience street basketball like never before with 3on3 FreeStyle on PS5! Enjoy upgraded graphics, faster gameplay, and immersive DualSense feedback. Choose unique characters, team up with friends, and dominate the court in intense 3v3 matches. Hit the virtual streets and show off your skills!
